Permissions Granularity
(https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj219771.aspx)
Site
Library or list
Folder
Document or item

Permissions are inherited from parent objects, unless fine-grained permissions are being implemented

Administrative Levels:
Farm Administrators Group
Windows Administrators Group
Service Application Administrators
Feature Administrators
Site Collection Administrators
Site Owners

Default Groups
-Group name- : -Default permission level-
Visitors     : Read
Members      : Edit
Owners       : Full Control
Viewers      : View Only

Site templates like the Publishing template, have unique groups just as in SP2010

Default Levels:
View Only
Limited Access
Read
Edit
Contribute
Design
Full Control

